      <data key="d1">AIRBORNE_PATHOGEN</data>
      <data key="d2">Coronavirus disease 2019 caused by SARS-CoV-2, transmitted via airborne droplets and aerosols, requiring protective measures in healthcare. | A respiratory infectious disease caused by the SARS-CoV-2 virus, transmitted primarily through airborne particles.</data>
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
