      <data key="d8">ACH</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DOSE</data>
      <data key="d10">Different window opening configurations affect the ACH, with front and rear windows open producing higher ACH than two rear windows open.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">e45568c3-e22e-4830-92f5-64de955e8aee_chunk_2</data>
      <data key="d14">e45568c3-e22e-4830-92f5-64de955e8aee</data>
    </edge>
