      <data key="d8">ACH</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DOSE</data>
      <data key="d10">Exhaust fan mode more than doubles ACH compared to supply mode, significantly improving ventilation rates in the bus.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.75</data>
